examples.sentence: 田中さんは望春という珍しい名字だ。(Tanaka-san wa Mochun to iu mezurashii myouji da.)
examples.translation: Mr. Tanaka has the rare surname Mochun.

etymology.value: The etymology of this surname is unclear due to its rarity. It may be derived from place names or historical figures.

usage_notes.explanation: This is a very uncommon Japanese surname. It is not typically encountered.
